parameters:
\nw[Taro]Looks like you can speak. Can you tell me your
name?
\nw[Rodrigo]I'm Rodrigo... I'm injured and can't move... Ugh!

\nw[Taro]It's Rodrigo, right? I'm glad I didn't mistake you
for someone else. I came to help on Fross's
request. Can you not walk?

\nw[Taro]I understand, but it's too big to carry alone.
Yellow, can you help me carry it?

\nw[Huma]Oh, it's a shame you're not a girl, but I guess
there's nothing we can do about it.

\nw[Uka]Someone seems to be over there on the right...
maybe?
\nw[Taro]Is that true? How do you know?

\nw[Taro]Alright, anyway, it's towards the back on the
right.

\nw[Taro]This isn't the right way, let's head in the
opposite direction.
